- 'masterpieces' and 'creations' refer to the images uploaded by users; 
- 'craftsman' and 'artist' refer to the users who uploaded the images;
- 'canvas size' refers to the 'area' of the images in pixels;
- 'contribution' refers to the image uploads, with the 'upload_date' being the date of contribution.

